#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.isinf.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.isinf"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:1 of
msgid "Test element-wise for positive or negative infinity."
msgstr "逐元素测试正无穷或负无穷。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns a boolean array of the same shape as `x`, True where ``x == "
"+/-inf``, otherwise False."
msgstr ""
"返回一个与`x`形状相同的布尔数组，其中``x == +/-inf``的位置为True，其他"
"位置为False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:6 of
msgid "Input values"
msgstr "输入值"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:8 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有能广播输入的形状。如果未提供或为`"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的tensor。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:13 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为True表示在该位置计算ufunc，值为False表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:18 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- For scalar input, the result is a new boolean with value True if"
" the input is positive or negative infinity; otherwise the value is "
"False.  For tensor input, the result is a boolean tensor with the same "
"shape as the input and the values are True where the corresponding "
"element of the input is positive or negative infinity; elsewhere the "
"values are False.  If a second argument was supplied the result is stored"
" there.  If the type of that array is a numeric type the result is "
"represented as zeros and ones, if the type is boolean then as False and "
"True, respectively.  The return value `y` is then a reference to that "
"tensor."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 对于标量输入，结果是一个新的布尔值，如果输入是正无穷或负无穷则为"
"True；否则为False。对于tensor输入，结果是一个与输入形状相同的布尔tensor，"
"其中输入元素为正无穷或负无穷的位置值为True，其他位置为False。如果提供了"
"第二个参数，则结果存储在那里。如果该数组的类型是数值类型，则结果表示为0和"
"1；如果类型是布尔类型，则分别表示为False和True。返回值`y`是该tensor的引用"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:18 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- For scalar input, the result is a new boolean with value True if"
" the input is positive or negative infinity; otherwise the value is "
"False."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:22 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For tensor input, the result is a boolean tensor with the same shape as "
"the input and the values are True where the corresponding element of the "
"input is positive or negative infinity; elsewhere the values are False.  "
"If a second argument was supplied the result is stored there.  If the "
"type of that array is a numeric type the result is represented as zeros "
"and ones, if the type is boolean then as False and True, respectively.  "
"The return value `y` is then a reference to that tensor."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 对于标量输入，结果是一个新的布尔值，如果输入是正无穷或负无穷则为"
"True；否则为False。对于tensor输入，结果是一个与输入形状相同的布尔tensor，"
"其中输入元素为正无穷或负无穷的位置值为True，其他位置为False。如果提供了"
"第二个参数，则结果存储在那里。如果该数组的类型是数值类型，则结果表示为0和"
"1；如果类型是布尔类型，则分别表示为False和True。返回值`y`是该tensor的引用"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:32 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`isneginf`, :py:obj:`isposinf`, :py:obj:`isnan`, "
":py:obj:`isfinite`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:35 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:36 of
msgid ""
"MaxFrame uses the IEEE Standard for Binary Floating-Point for Arithmetic "
"(IEEE 754)."
msgstr "MaxFrame使用IEEE二进制浮点数算术标准（IEEE 754）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isinf.isinf:39 of
msgid ""
"Errors result if the second argument is supplied when the first argument "
"is a scalar, or if the first and second arguments have different shapes."
msgstr ""
"如果第一个参数是标量时提供了第二个参数，或者第一个和第二个参数的形状不同"
"，则会导致错误。"

